<p><strong>Languages</strong> Auran, Common</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 3 (700 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Spellcasting.</em></strong> The Skyweaver is a 6th-level spellcaster. Its spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 13, +5 to hit with spell attacks). It knows the following sorcerer spells:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Cantrips (at will): blade ward, light, message, ray of frost, shocking grasp</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>1st level (4 slots): feather fall, mage armor, witch bolt</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>2nd level (3 slots): gust of wind, invisibility</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>3rd level (3 slots): fly, lightning bolt</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Dagger.</em></strong> Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 20/60 ft., one target. Hit: 3 (1d4 + 1) piercing damage.</p>

